  m_text: 'In recent years, many of us have experienced stress and pressure due to
    emergency situations and war.


    This training experience is designed to help
    improve your ability to function under stress.


    Please connect your smartwatch.
    In each simulation, your physiological response is measured and at the end you
    receive practical recommendations for next time.'
