    Help anytime for current task instructions.'
  helpSimulation1: "Simulation 1 - Emergency preparedness\n\n1) Collect three essential
    items inside the home:\n\u2022 Watet Bottle\n\u2022 Flash Light\n\u2022 Radio\n\n2)
