  helpSimulation2: "Simulation 2 \u2013 First Aid Under Pressure\n\n1) Approach the
    wounded person. press E to start.\n\n2) Start treatment and follow step order.\nHow
    to complete treatment:\nFollow the on-screen steps. Press the required keys in
    order (1 \u2192 2 \u2192 3) until treatment is complete."
  pauseKey: 27
